quran[7{c,v,t}:
40,34,"is se pehlay yousuf tumahray paas bayyaynaat le kar aeye thay magar tum unn ki layi hui taleem ki taraf se shak hi mein parre rahay phir jab unn ka intqaal ho gaya to tum ne kaha ab unn ke baad Allah koi rasool hargiz nah beje ga"" isi terhan Allah unn sab logon ko gumraahi mein daal deta hai jo hadd se guzarnay walay aur shakki hotay hain"
40,35,aur Allah ki ayaat mein jhagrre karte hain baghair is ke ke un ke paas koi sanad ya Daleel aayi ho yeh rawayya Allah aur imaan laane walon ke nazdeek sakht mabghoz (bezari ki baat) hai isi terhan Allah har munkiro Jabbar ke dil par thpah laga deta hai
40,36,"firaon ne kaha"" ae Haman , mere liye aik buland imarat bana taakay mein raastoon taq poanch sakun"
40,37,"asmano ke raastoon taq, aur moose ke khuda ko jhaank kar daikhon mujhe to yeh moose jhoota hi maloom hota hai"" is terhan firaon ke liye is ki bad amli khushnuma bana di gayi aur woh raah raast se rok diya gaya firaon ki saari chaal baazi ( uss ki apni ) tabahi ke rasta hi mein sirf hui"
40,38,"woh shakhs jo imaan laya tha, bola"" ae meri qoum ke logo, meri baat manu, mein tumhe sahih rasta batata hon"
40,39,"ae qoum, yeh duniya ki zindagi to chand roza hai, hamesha ke qiyam ki jagah akhirat hi hai"
40,40,"jo buraiee kere ga uss ko itna hi badla miley ga jitni uss ne buraiee ki ho gi aur jo naik amal kere ga, khuwa woh mard ho ya aurat, bashart e kay ho woh momin, aisay sab log jannat mein daakhil hon ge jahan unn ko be hisaab rizaq diya jaye ga"
